snippet.title: DiNO LAND MAGiC on UNiCORN CATCH!!  Adley and Navey play our Lava Volcano Tycoon, a new Roblox Game
snippet.description:
HEY EVERYBODY!! ðŸŽµiT'S RAiNiNG UNiCORNS! FROM OUT OF THE SKY!!ðŸŽµðŸŽµ

JOIN THE FAM - https://www.youtube.com/@GforGaming

Can we save all the unicorns? Can we build an entire dino-land? Can we run a unicorn waterpark? I DON'T KNOW!
Have you tried our Unicorn Catch Tycoon on Roblox yet?

But we'll find out in todays BRAND NEW episode of G for Gaming with some of your favorite hosts, Adley, Navey, Dad and Saedie! We have a huge surprise that some of you may have already been playing with or testing out! Navey wanted to show Adley her new exciting update in Unicorn Catch Tycoon on Roblox! Our apps team have been working really hard to add so many new cool things in our Roblox games that fans like YOU have suggested or even ideas we came up with on our own!

Navey surprised Adley at first in real life by tossing a stuffy unicorn at her and trying to scare her and then showed her a sweet, cute little pink heart that Navey left on her computer for her! Then, Navey told Adley that there are new updates and secrets inside of our Unicorn Catch Roblox game! So as fast as we could, we hopped on Roblox and started checking out all of these new awesome secrets! Navey and Adley both finished their Unicorn castles and traveled to the next world which was... drumroll please... DINO LAND! That's right! There were giant dinosaurs playing with our friend unicorns and we had to catch enough unicorns so that we could build out all of the Dino park! There were so many cool things, there's a huge T-rex with a unicorn riding him, there's a volcano with lava and even a lava obby that's inside of the volcano! But, in case you're really hot after being around all of that lava, don't worry because the next world after the dino land is an awesome, cute Unicorn Water Park!

We showed off some of the hidden codes you can find to get extra magic and surprises! You'll have to look all over the place because they are hidden in the sneakiest places of all time! Tell us your ideas for the game and it just might make it into the game in a future update!

Thanks for watching!! BYE! PSSSSSSSSHHHHHHHHHHHHH
